# 1. 不影响函数调用, 增加参数

先看以下函数调用:

```go
package main

import "fmt"

func ExecUser(name string, age int) {
	fmt.Println("name:", name, "age:", age)
}

func main() {
	ExecUser("levonfly", 9)
}

